Dotfiles
========

Curated configuration files and installer for i3/polybar/kitty/zsh/neovim.

Install (recommended)::

    git clone https://github.com/0xjah/Dotfiles.git ~/Dotfiles
    cd ~/Dotfiles
    chmod +x install.sh
    ./install.sh 

Top-level contents::

    .config/i3  .config/polybar  .config/kitty  .config/nvim  .config/rofi
.config/dunst  .config/i3blocks  .config/picom  .zshrc  install.sh

Contributing
------------

Issues and pull requests are welcome. Please open them on GitHub.

